            <h6>Aren't there a bunch of Final Fantasy websites?</h6>
            <p class="text-dark">Exactly. That means there's a bunch of different sources of the same/similar data.</p>
            <p class="text-dark">The goal is to provide a single source of data that any website can consume and use. When new games come out it could take some time for a variety of websites to catch up. With the API it could be updated once and the new information can then be consumed by any number of websites at the same time.</p>
